<p style="text-align:center;margin:0;padding:0;"> Checks hosts with LIFECYCLE=Production in OEM </p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin:0;padding:0;"> Checks QA and DV hosts for BVM and BMM </p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin:0;padding:0;"> If Diskgroup total size greater than  60TB, then the disk group threshold is 90% or min 10 TB space should be available, whichever is lower.</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin:0;padding:0;"> If Diskgroup total size less than  60TB, then the disk group threshold is 80% or min 4 TB space should be available, whichever is lower.</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin:0;padding:0;"> If Diskgroup total size less than  6 TB, then the disk group threshold is 80% or min 2 TB space should be available, whichever is lower.</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin:0;padding:0;"> Check SKIPs ACFS Diskgroups</p>
<p style="text-align:center;margin:0;padding:0;"> Check SKIPs *CTLLOG* Diskgroups</p>
